{"tid":850412,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"BLACKPINK刷新K-POP MV點擊破4億最速紀錄","createTime":"2018-10-06T12:57:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-06T14:50:33.000Z","uid":74065,"like":8,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"76bfb097aa18da609d096488ff08e1286a33b43a","tid":850412,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T12:57:18.000Z","msg":"【大紀元2018年10月06日訊】（大紀元記者曾薇心編譯報導）韓國女團BLACKPINK於6月15日發行首張迷你專輯《SQUARE UP》，當天同步公開的主打歌《DDU-DU DDU-DU》官方MV於YouTube觀看次數於今（6）日突破4億。<br />\n<br />\nBLACKPINK《DDU DU DDU DU》官方MV的觀看次數，此前於8月23日以公開68天的時間突破3億點擊，超越BTS防彈少年團的《DNA》（費時約5個月）所創下的成績，成為K-POP「最快突破3億點擊」的MV。<br />\n<br />\n而今日該MV又於韓國時間早上10點，以費時112天的成績突破4億點擊。該成績較過去的紀錄快了五個月。<br />\n<br />\n《DDU DU DDU DU》自突破1,000萬點擊起，就接連創下韓國女團以最短時間突破各個千萬點擊大關、以及最快突破1億點擊的紀錄。而自2億點擊開始，就已不只侷限在韓國女團，而是接連創下K-POP的最佳紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n此外，BLACKPINK的官方YouTube訂閱人數也已突破1,000萬，截至本稿寫成為止已有超過1,235萬人訂閱。該成績也讓她們成為「於YouTube擁有最多訂閱人數的K-POP團體」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBLACKPINK&gt;世界彈<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20c25bf1562f0bfec8b6524f214393969a15e4b3","tid":850412,"uid":165368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T13:00:51.000Z","msg":"好!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nps只係過咗dna<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d6d1b53775da2bff0f2edea0785d7a4e6bcb345","tid":850412,"uid":213300,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T13:35:27.000Z","msg":"宜家k pop一大堆買view<br />\nblackpink 頭一日三千幾萬<br />\nbts idol 頭一日 五千幾萬<br />\n點同以前 youtube唔盛行嗰時<br />\n咁樣破紀錄有咩意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77b8d6f2eadf20365501b1cbba5adf1f25132555","tid":850412,"uid":120791,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T13:36:59.000Z","msg":"2NE1 笑而不語"},{"pid":"a355a82bd5a8a395ebfa24a4ccfd59070a06d0d2","tid":850412,"uid":52073,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T14:00:07.000Z","msg":"天團twice呢?"},{"pid":"e9b5235143e272df02bbc897a200d2dad914a45e","tid":850412,"uid":74065,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a355a82bd5a8a395ebfa24a4ccfd59070a06d0d2","tid":850412,"uid":52073,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T14:00:07.000Z","msg":"天團twice呢?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T14:05:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/30/080647_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F30%2F080647_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=e9d187d8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3cfa6da258e9806b2a188a6a5c6f7955c806d8f5","tid":850412,"uid":2781,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T14:31:33.000Z","msg":"呢首歌我竟然一次都冇點擊過&hellip;"},{"pid":"52f68eb6cf2ec9fc5563876857a889e9fd940a15","tid":850412,"uid":63057,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T14:50:33.000Z","msg":"TT一早過左4億<br />\nTWICE係第一個過4億嘅kpop 組合"}]}